---
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<section id="rrhh" class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white border-t border-neutral-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-red-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">RRHH</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Creemos en la cultura del trabajo, en la que todos podamos prosperar. Si Usted tiene potencial y desea crecer, en nuestra empresa encontrará el ámbito ideal para desarrollarse. Enviar Currículum Vittae por e-mail:
      </p>
      <a
        href={`mailto:${SITE.contact.email}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-brand-red text-white font-semibold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-brand-red-dark transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-red/25 hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        {SITE.contact.email}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
